	Fixed some issues raised by unit tests.

	* MonoDevelop.Projects.Dom.Parser/ProjectDomService.cs: Removed the
	lastUpdateSize cache because it is not 100% reliable and it is
	problematic when we want to force a file reparse (e.g. to resolve
	types which were unresolved in previous parsings).

	* MonoDevelop.Projects.Dom/DomType.cs: Little optimization.

	* MonoDevelop.Projects.mdp: Updated.

