	fixes in GetSubclasses. It now supports inner types and generic types
	much better. All covered by unit tests.

	* MonoDevelop.Projects.Dom.Serialization/NamespaceEntry.cs: Moved
	GetName to ParserDatabase since it is now being used in other
	classes.

