	* MonoDevelop.Projects.Dom.Parser/ProjectDomService.cs: Load the help
	tree asynchronously. Reduces startup time.

2008-11-14  Lluis Sanchez Gual  <lluis@novell.com>

	* MonoDevelop.Projects.Dom.Parser/ProjectDomService.cs: Don't crash if
	something goes wrong with Monodoc initialization. Removed
	UpdateReferences call in Load(). This call was added to fix bug
	#427285, but this is the wrong fix. Everything seems to work fine
	without it, and it is a performance bottleneck.

